headline.main: ROME MANOEUVRE FOR PEACE IS SEEN; Moves of Fascist Ex-Official and Lyon Cardinal Suggest Overtures to France ROME MANOEUVRE FOR PEACE IS SEEN

lead_paragraph: PORTBOU, Spain, Jan. 31 -- It is conceded on all sides that the war is about to take a new turn, but is that turn necessarily military? There are some observers who believe the change might conceivably be brought about through diplomatic and political channels.
abstract: Pope Pius reptd endorsing Axis grant of separate peace???proposal to France
